<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-7">Parking</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Car Parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Cycle parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Disabled parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContentc9d768a96bf243f3a098fa3ebf53df50">
</div>
<p>The Trust operates a pay on foot system – similar to those of the Grosvenor Centre, Liverpool 1, and Manchester Airport. Many patients and visitors are exempt from paying the charge, including patients on certain benefits, disabled badge holders attending an appointment, some regular patients and families of patients in certain units.</p>
<p>From July 3rd 2011, the following charges apply:</p>
<p>First 30 minutes     FREE</p>
<p>up to 5 hours            £3</p>
<p>5 to 8 hours              £5</p>
<p>More than 8 hours   £7</p>
